SOURCE

https://grail.cs.washington.edu/projects/AudioToObama/siggraph17_obama.pdf

AGENT

University of Washington

GOAL

Synthesise a person's voice and vocal mannerisms

DATA

Footage of President Obama's weekly address

METHODS

Association of audio features with mouth shapes, CGI and 3D pose matching

RESULTS

Photorealistic video of President Obama speaking, generated by the algorithm

COMMENTS

